caller_intent: Tracy from Alliance Insurance is trying to confirm whether a liability claim (involving a tree branch falling on a vehicle) was successfully filed with Berkeley Aspire, as they did not receive an expected email confirmation.
resolution_steps: Agent Alejandro requested the policy number, callback number, and claim details.
Alejandro apologized for the delay and explained the system's limited access to claim data.
He confirmed the claim was filed and scheduled a follow-up to verify its status.
Provided a 24-48 hour timeframe for resolution and assured Tracy of prompt action.
knowledge_required: Claim filing process for property/liability claims
Internal system limitations for claims reporting line
summary: Tracy from Alliance Insurance contacted Berkeley Aspire to confirm a liability claim was filed after not receiving an email confirmation. Agent Alejandro verified the claim details, acknowledged the system's limitations, and scheduled a follow-up to resolve the issue within 24-48 hours. Tracy was satisfied with the resolution plan.
